snippet.title: Lusa the Cathead // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game: https://gern05.itch.io/lusa-the-cathead

Lusa the Cathead is an action platformer game where you get to play as a cute cat-head-looking creature named Lusa! Jump your way through the stages, collect orbs and break capsules while avoiding obstacles... and from now on, gathering polymers and megamers to gain score! This game is very customizable, with possibility for not only custom stages, but custom characters with unique mechanics, powered by Lua scripting, free for any modifications!

Developed by Team CIRCULAR
